        <p class="style82"> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em> <strong><em>        <strong> Where did all that money go? </strong> </em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong></em></strong><em><em><em><em><em><em><em><em><em><em>Standards manage everything &ndash; including how your money is recorded and transferred, and how corporations are expected today to report to regulators. The following items provide a sampling of current standards efforts in this area. </em></em></em></em></em></em></em></em></em></em></p></td>
